---
title: Turkey Burrito Bowls with Avocado Pico De Gallo and Cilantro-Lime Rice
description: Tasty turkey takes centre stage with cilantro-lime rice as its co-star. The avocado pico de gallo makes a great extra in this soon-to-be award-winning dish!
